  "prompt": "How can I change my name in Clash of Clan?",
  "response": "Changing your name in Clash of Clans is a straightforward process. Here are the steps you need to follow:\n\n1. **Open Clash of Clans**: Launch the game on your device.\n\n2. **Settings Menu**: Tap on the gear icon (usually located at the top right corner) to open the settings menu.\n\n3. **Change Name**: In the settings menu, you'll see an option that says \"Change Name.\" Tap on this option.\n\n4. **Follow Prompts**: You'll be prompted to enter your new name. Enter the name you want, and confirm it.\n\nIt's important to note that you can change your name only once for free. Subsequent changes will cost Gems, the in-game currency. Make sure to choose a name you're happy with!\n\nAdditionally, ensure that your new name adheres to Supercell\u2019s guidelines and does not contain any inappropriate or offensive words.\n\nIf you encounter any issues or have further questions, you might need to contact Supercell support for assistance.",
